      "para_id": "Q001795.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Amar-Suena , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , built for ( Nanna ) the jail in Urim . The name of this jail is \" Amar-Suena is the beloved of Nanna \"."
    }
